        <section id="market-analysis" class="animated-section"> <h2><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> 2. MARKET ANALYSIS</h2>
            <h3><i class="fas fa-industry fa-xs" style="margin-right: 8px;"></i> Industry Overview</h3>
            <p>The digital products market continues to experience robust growth, with Etsy maintaining its position as a premier marketplace for creative digital goods. With over 96 million active buyers and a marketplace revenue exceeding $2.8 billion in 2024, Etsy represents an ideal platform for launching digital product businesses.</p>
            <h3><i class="fas fa-users fa-xs" style="margin-right: 8px;"></i> Target Market Profile</h3>
            <p>PixelCrafted Studio will focus on three key customer segments:</p>
            <ol>
                 <li><strong>Productivity Enthusiasts (Primary)</strong><ul><li>Age: 25-45</li><li>Gender: 75% female, 25% male</li><li>Characteristics: Busy professionals, parents, students with ADHD/focus challenges</li><li>Pain points: Overwhelm, disorganization, difficulty maintaining systems</li></ul></li>
                 <li><strong>Small Business Owners</strong><ul><li>Age: 28-55</li><li>Characteristics: Entrepreneurs, freelancers, small teams</li><li>Pain points: Limited design resources, brand inconsistency, time constraints</li></ul></li>
                 <li><strong>Home Organization Enthusiasts</strong><ul><li>Age: 30-65</li><li>Characteristics: Homemakers, working parents, retirees</li><li>Pain points: Paper clutter, managing household tasks, seasonal organization</li></ul></li>
            </ol>

            <h3><i class="fas fa-search-dollar fa-xs" style="margin-right: 8px;"></i> Competitive Analysis</h3>
            <table>
                <thead><tr><th><i class="fas fa-chess-knight"></i> Competitor Category</th><th><i class="fas fa-thumbs-up"></i> Strengths</th><th><i class="fas fa-thumbs-down"></i> Weaknesses</th><th><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Our Advantage</th></tr></thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr><td>Established Etsy Sellers</td><td>Brand recognition, Reviews</td><td>Often generic designs, Limited personalization</td><td>AI customization, ADHD-specific niche</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>Large Digital Template Companies</td><td>Wide selection, Professional design</td><td>Higher prices, Less specialized</td><td>Focused product strategy, Automation reducing costs</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>Solo Creators</td><td>Unique aesthetics, Loyal fans</td><td>Inconsistent quality, Limited SKUs</td><td>AI consistency, Scalable production</td></tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <h3><i class="fas fa-fire fa-xs" style="margin-right: 8px;"></i> Market Trends & Category Popularity</h3>
