            </div>
            <p>The digital product marketplace is evolving with several key trends that PixelCrafted Studio will capitalize on:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check fa-xs" style="color: var(--accent-color); margin-right: 5px;"></i> Increased demand for personalized products</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check fa-xs" style="color: var(--accent-color); margin-right: 5px;"></i> Growing awareness and acceptance of ADHD and neurodiversity</li>
