            <h3><i class="fas fa-box-open fa-xs" style="margin-right: 8px;"></i> Product Line Focus</h3>
             <p>Instead of launching with five product categories simultaneously, PixelCrafted will focus initially on two high-demand, high-margin categories:</p>
             <p><strong>Phase 1 (Months 1-3): Core Products</strong></p><ol><li><strong>ADHD-Optimized Planners & Productivity Tools</strong><ul><li>Daily focus planners with dopamine tracking</li><li>Task batching templates for executive function support</li><li>Time-blocking systems with visual cues</li><li>Habit trackers with variable reward systems</li></ul></li><li><strong>Minimalist Social Media Templates</strong><ul><li>Instagram carousel templates (educational focus)</li><li>Pinterest pin templates (productivity/organization themes)</li><li>Content planning systems</li><li>Caption frameworks and prompts</li></ul></li></ol>
             <p><strong>Phase 2 (Months 4-6): Expansion Products</strong></p><ol><li><strong>Wall Art Collections</strong><ul><li>Minimalist abstract prints</li><li>Productivity affirmations</li><li>Focus-enhancing mandalas</li></ul></li><li><strong>Basic Branding Kits</strong><ul><li>Logo templates for solopreneurs</li><li>Color palette guides</li><li>Social media profile templates</li></ul></li></ol>

