        <section id="marketing-sales" class="animated-section"> <h2><i class="fas fa-bullhorn"></i> 5. MARKETING & SALES PLAN</h2>
            <h3><i class="fas fa-store fa-xs" style="margin-right: 8px;"></i> Platform Strategy</h3>
            <p>While Etsy will serve as the primary sales channel, PixelCrafted Studio will implement a multi-channel approach to maximize visibility:</p>
            <ol><li><strong>Etsy Store (Primary)</strong><ul><li>Optimized listings with strategic keywords</li><li>Regular shop updates to boost algorithm visibility</li><li>Strategic use of Etsy ads focused on converting products</li></ul></li><li><strong>Pinterest Marketing (Secondary)</strong><ul><li>Content-rich pins linking to products</li><li>Strategic board organization</li><li>Participation in group boards</li></ul></li><li><strong>Email Marketing</strong><ul><li>Lead magnet: Free simplified planner</li><li>Weekly newsletter with productivity tips</li><li>Exclusive discounts and early access</li></ul></li></ol>
            <h3><i class="far fa-calendar-check fa-xs" style="margin-right: 8px;"></i> Marketing Calendar</h3>
            <p><strong>Month 1:</strong></p><ul><li>Etsy shop launch with 10 core products</li><li>Pinterest business account setup</li><li>Lead magnet creation</li></ul>
            <p><strong>Month 2:</strong></p><ul><li>Begin Etsy Ads with $100 budget</li><li>Launch 2 new Pinterest boards weekly</li><li>Email welcome sequence development</li></ul>
            <p><strong>Month 3:</strong></p><ul><li>Increase to 25 total products</li><li>Micro-influencer outreach (5 partners)</li><li>Weekly email content calendar</li></ul>
            <p><strong>Month 4-6:</strong></p><ul><li>Product bundling and tiered pricing</li><li>Automated customer review requests</li><li>Seasonal product launches</li></ul>
            <h3><i class="fas fa-tag fa-xs" style="margin-right: 8px;"></i> Pricing Strategy</h3>
            <img src="https://placehold.co/800x300/f5a623/ffffff?text=Pricing+Strategy+Visual" alt="Pricing Tier Strategy Placeholder" class="placeholder-img">
            <p>PixelCrafted Studio will implement a three-tier pricing structure:</p><ul><li><strong>Basic Products:</strong> $3.99-$7.99</li><li><strong>Premium Products:</strong> $9.99-$14.99</li><li><strong>Bundles/Collections:</strong> $17.99-$29.99</li></ul>
            <p>Pricing will be continually optimized based on:</p><ul><li>Conversion rate analysis</li><li>Competitor pricing</li><li>Seasonal demand fluctuations</li><li>Customer feedback</li></ul>
